CAPE TOWN - A beachfront apartment block in Sea Point was evacuated on Wednesday after a fire broke out on the fourth floor.The City s Fire and Rescue Services said the affected apartment block is called Mimosa Court and is situated on Beach Road.Building alight, beach road, sea point. All emergency crews on scene. pic.twitter.com/4WXhvxALvT#AATrafficCPT Sea Point ROAD CLOSED between Arthurs Road and Church Road due to a BUILDING FIRE Church Road - SouthboundThe City s Theo Layne said they responded just before midday. Two persons sustained minor smoke inhalation -- one man and a woman -- were treated by ambulance staff .The cause of the fire is being investigated.African News Agency